# Force LF line endings in the working tree regardless of core.autocrlf.
# Biome's formatter expects LF (its default); with autocrlf=true on Windows,
# every checkout produced CRLF files and `npm run lint` failed on all of
# them with format-only errors. eol=lf makes checkout deterministic on the
# Windows 11 streaming machine and everywhere else.
* text=auto eol=lf
